description.narrative: This activity (Surge Staff & CHASE OT) is a component of Multi-Year Humanitarian Programme in Pakistan reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £522,355. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: CANADEM, Crown Agents Limited, Norwegian Refugee Council, Palladium International Ltd (UK). The start date is 16-06-2014 and the end date is 31-12-2022.
